'''蘇菲亞·克莉絲汀娜·阿莫魯索''' ('''Sophia Christina Amoruso'''，{{Bd|1984年|4月20日}})<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.californiabirthindex.org/birth/sophia_christina_amoruso_born_1984_16164751|title=Sophia Christina Amoruso|accessdate=September 11, 2016|work=California Birth Index|archive-date=2019-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191101225112/https://www.californiabirthindex.org/birth/sophia_christina_amoruso_born_1984_16164751|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，是一位[[美國|美國]]的[[企業家|企業家]]。她曾在2016年被[[福布斯|富比世]]評選為[[世界|世界]]上最[[富豪|有錢]]的[[創業家|白手起家]][[女性|女性]]之一<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/clareoconnor/2016/06/01/nasty-gal-sophia-amoruso-richest-women-net-worth/#7684777044e1|title=Nasty Gal's Sophia Amoruso Hits Richest Self-Made Women List With $280 Million Fortune|accessdate=September 10, 2016|author=O'Connor, Clare|date=June 1, 2016|work=Forbes|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117224447/https://www.forbes.com/sites/clareoconnor/2016/06/01/nasty-gal-sophia-amoruso-richest-women-net-worth/#7684777044e1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 

== 生平 ==

=== 早年生活 ===
蘇菲亞·阿莫魯索在1984年出生於加州[[聖地牙哥_(加利福尼亞州)|聖地牙哥]]；她有來自[[希臘|希臘]]、[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]與[[義大利|義大利]]的[[血統|血統]]。

自小，她成長於一個信奉[[希臘正教會|希臘東正教]]的[[家庭|家庭]]。<ref name="greek2">{{cite web|url=http://www.pappaspost.com/greek-nasty-gals-sophia-amoruso-deconstructed/|title=The Greek in Nasty Gal’s Sophia Amoruso Deconstructed|accessdate=September 10, 2016|author=Pappas, Gregory|date=May 7, 2014|work=Pappas Post|archive-date=2020-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129232556/https://www.pappaspost.com/greek-nasty-gals-sophia-amoruso-deconstructed/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在被診斷出患有[[注意力不足過動症|注意力缺失症]]之後，她旋即輟學[[在家自學|回家自學]]。她起先在一家[[賽百味|賽百味]]餐廳工作，後來陸續在[[書店|書店]]和唱片行等處任職。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=djgJH3oYIoE|title=Sophia Amoruso Discusses Her Book, "Nasty Galaxy"|accessdate=October 4, 2016|date=October 15, 2016|work=America Online|series=BUILD}}</ref>後來，她在父母離婚後搬至[[沙加緬度_(加利福尼亞州)|沙加緬度]]定居。<ref name="mj">{{cite web|url=http://www.msnbc.com/morning-joe/excerpt-sophia-amorusos-girlboss|title=Sophia Amoruso is taking your questions|accessdate=October 15, 2016|author=Morning Joe Staff|date=May 28, 2014|work=MSBC|archive-date=2020-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200226082649/http://www.msnbc.com/morning-joe/excerpt-sophia-amorusos-girlboss|dead-url=no}}</ref>當時，她在[[美國西岸|美國西岸]]過著四處流浪的生活；有時[[搭便車|搭便車]]，有時在[[垃圾|垃圾]]堆裡翻找可用物品，更有時[[偷竊|偷竊]]。<ref name=":02" />

2003年，她居住於[[波特蘭_(俄勒岡州)|波特蘭]]，並在進行偷竊時被逮著；該店損失預防部門隨即向她處以[[罰金|罰金]]，她也由此停止偷竊行為。<ref name=":02">{{Cite book|title=#GIRLBOSS|last=Amoruso|first=Sophia|publisher=the Penguin Group|year=2014|isbn=978-0-399-16927-4|location=New York|pages=3}}</ref>

在發現[[鼠蹊部|鼠蹊部]]患有[[疝|疝]]之後，她搬遷至[[舊金山|舊金山]]以購買醫療保險支付其必要醫療<ref name="mj2">{{cite web|url=http://www.msnbc.com/morning-joe/excerpt-sophia-amorusos-girlboss|title=Sophia Amoruso is taking your questions|accessdate=October 15, 2016|author=Morning Joe Staff|date=May 28, 2014|work=MSBC|archive-date=2020-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200226082649/http://www.msnbc.com/morning-joe/excerpt-sophia-amorusos-girlboss|dead-url=no}}</ref>；隨後，她一邊在[[社區學院|社區學院]]就讀，一邊在[[舊金山藝術大學|舊金山藝術大學]][[兼差|兼差]]檢查[[學生證|學生證]]件。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.fashionschooldaily.com/index.php/2014/07/07/the-girlboss-of-nasty-gal/|title=The #GIRLBOSS of Nasty Gal Sophia Amoruso|date=2014-07-07|newspaper=Fashion School Daily, School of Fashion Blog at Academy of Art University|accessdate=2017-06-03|language=en-US|archive-date=2017-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171114222645/http://www.fashionschooldaily.com/index.php/2014/07/07/the-girlboss-of-nasty-gal/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 事業生涯 ===
在舊金山藝術大學擔任[[保全|保全]]時，她開了間名為「Nasty Gal Vintage」的[[eBay|eBay]][[網路商店|網路商店]]（該店命名源自[[放克|放克]]歌手及[[時尚潮流|時尚]]人物{{Link-en|Betty Davis|Betty Davis}}於1975年發行的[[專輯|專輯]]）。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.somamagazine.com/cool-boutiques/|title=SOMA Magazine  » Archive   » Cool Boutiques|accessdate=2017-06-03|last=Magazine|first=SOMA|work=www.somamagazine.com|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210513132512/http://www.somamagazine.com/cool-boutiques/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="mj2" /><ref name=":0">{{Cite news|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/business/20130422/c22nasty/zh-hant/|title=「勁爆女孩」，一個灰姑娘的創業故事|date=2013-04-24|newspaper=紐約時報中文網 國際縱覽|accessdate=2017-06-03|language=zh|archive-date=2020-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202062254/https://cn.nytimes.com/business/20130422/c22nasty/zh-hant/|dead-url=no}}</ref>不久，Nasty Gal在[[社群媒體|社群媒體]]上培養出了一群由年輕[[女性|女性]]組成的忠實[[粉絲|追隨者]]；自2008年至2011年，其[[營業額|營業額]]由約22.3萬[[美元|美元]]成長至近2.3[[千萬|千萬]]美元<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.inc.com/30under30/donna-fenn/nasty-gal-sophia-amoruso-2013.html|title=Unselfconsciously Sexy Style|date=Tue May 28 08:00:00 2013|newspaper=Inc.com|accessdate=2017-06-03|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170915090534/https://www.inc.com/30under30/donna-fenn/nasty-gal-sophia-amoruso-2013.html|archive-date=2017-09-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2013年，她在《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》上被稱作「一位科技界的[[灰姑娘|灰姑娘]]」<ref name=":0" />，《{{Link-en|Inc.雜誌|Inc. (magazine)}}》同時也將她列入其「30 under 30 」名單<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.inc.com/ss/donna-fenn/30-under-30-meet-the-winners-2013#1|title=Meet the 30 Under 30, Class of 2013|date=Tue May 14 09:03:11 2013|newspaper=Inc.com|accessdate=2017-06-03|language=en|archive-date=2020-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202062245/https://www.inc.com/ss/donna-fenn/30-under-30-meet-the-winners-2013#1|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，《[[商業內幕|商業內幕]]》更將她評為「現存最性感[[CEO|CEO]]」<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/the-sexiest-ceos-alive-2013-9?op=1|title=The Sexiest CEOs Alive!|newspaper=Business Insider|accessdate=2017-06-03|language=en|archive-date=2020-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202062246/https://www.businessinsider.com/the-sexiest-ceos-alive-2013-9?op=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>；同年，她的[[自傳|自傳]]''#GIRLBOSS''由[[企鵝出版集團|企鵝出版集團]]旗下Portfolio出版社發行。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/01/11/style/who-will-be-americas-next-top-mentor.html|title=Who Will Be America’s Next Top Mentor?|last=Jacobs|first=Alexandra|date=2015-01-09|newspaper=The New York Times|accessdate=2017-06-03|language=en-US|issn=0362-4331|archive-date=2020-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202062234/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/01/11/style/who-will-be-americas-next-top-mentor.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2015年1月12日，她宣布辭去在Nasty Gal的CEO職務。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://recode.net/2015/01/12/nasty-gal-founder-sophia-amoruso-steps-down-as-ceo-of-fashion-retailer/|title=Nasty Gal Founder Sophia Amoruso Hands Over CEO Role|accessdate=2017-06-03|author=|date=2015-01-13|publisher=Re/code|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150113021118/http://recode.net/2015/01/12/nasty-gal-founder-sophia-amoruso-steps-down-as-ceo-of-fashion-retailer/|archivedate=2015-01-13}}</ref>

2016年11月，Nasty Gal聲請[[破產保護|破產保護]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.omnimgt.com/sblite/templates/a/Default.aspx?clientId=CsgAAncz%2b6YCoU%2fCoCD4yMeA7cTfRFBHjBwUI6j1RwM2%2fzin%2bFcfYeAyA1QRxI9T%2fvd7OJxp3go%3d|title=Nasty Gal Bankruptcy|accessdate=15 November 2016|last1=Omni|first1=Rust|website=Nasty Gal Inc - bankruptcy|archive-date=2018-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180723070047/http://www.omnimgt.com/sblite/templates/a/Default.aspx?clientId=CsgAAncz%2B6YCoU%2FCoCD4yMeA7cTfRFBHjBwUI6j1RwM2%2Fzin%2BFcfYeAyA1QRxI9T%2Fvd7OJxp3go%3D|dead-url=no}}</ref>，她辭去[[执行董事|執行董事長]]職務。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.recode.net/2016/11/9/13578718/nasty-gal-is-expected-to-file-for-bankruptcy|title=Nasty Gal is expected to file for bankruptcy|accessdate=2017-06-03|date=2016-11-09|last=Swisher|first=Kara|work=Recode|archive-date=2018-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180624040040/https://www.recode.net/2016/11/9/13578718/nasty-gal-is-expected-to-file-for-bankruptcy|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2017年4月，由她的自傳改編而成的電視影集《[[正妹CEO|正妹CEO]]》開始在[[Netflix|Netflix]]播出。

